These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
Music-Genre: hip-hop, country
Beverage: mirinda, soy-milk
1. Beverage:mirinda is in an even position##4
2. Beverage:soy-milk == Music-Genre:country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | country | hip-hop |
| Beverage     | soy-milk    | mirinda   |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
Movie-Genre: zombie, superhero
City: marseilles, san-francisco
1. City:marseilles is in an odd position##4
2. Movie-Genre:superhero is on the left of Movie-Genre:zombie##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | zombie        |
| City      | marseilles  | san-francisco |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
Beverage: lemonade, fanta
Flower: poppy, daffodil
1. Flower:poppy is in an odd position##4
2. Beverage:fanta is on the left of Beverage:lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Beverage   | fanta    | lemonade |
| Flower   | poppy | daffodil |

